item.title: ~¬If you Answer i Rate u¬~

item.description:
@_Vengeance wrote:

[quote=“Mod Umair, post:6, topic:230489”][quote author=jc22493 link=topic=303452.msg2433911#msg2433911 date=1221073865]
1: Don’t make useless titles and say “I’ll rate you.”
2: Like Jarnohh said, it’s REP, not rate.
3: Write in correct grammar and format so that it is easier to comprehend your inquiries…
4: There is no reason you cannot use No-Ip.
5: Did you set your environmental variables?
6: Did you set your static IP?
7: Do NOT use Hamachi, as it lags, and not many people play on Hamachi.

Good luck with your server…
It’s probably going to be 100% leeched anyways…
[/quote]

yeah, thats what you think thanks for your help.
im too certain about the leeched part…

then again i guess your a noob…soo…eerrrr…i understand.[/quote]

You’re obviously retarded if you can’t even work out how to host the server, so I wouldn’t be downing others if I was you.
